"title": "8460: pleasing God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8460: pleasing god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An essential aspect of the life of believers that is more than a matter of external observance, but a total and heartfelt commitment to God.</p>\n<h2>Pleasing God is commanded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8-Eph5:10\">EPH 5:8–5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:9\">2CO 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:8\">GAL 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1\">1TH 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:3\">1TI 2:1–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a></p>\n<h2>It is more important to please God than to please people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:10\">GAL 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15-Gal1:16\">GAL 1:15–1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:4\">1TH 2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Pleasing God involves inward attitudes, not simply external observance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:17\">1CH 29:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:16-Ps51:17\">PSA 51:16–51:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17-Rom14:18\">ROM 14:17–14:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:4\">PSA 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30-Ps69:31\">PSA 69:30–69:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:10-Ps147:11\">PSA 147:10–147:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:20\">PRO 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:8\">PRO 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:4\">ECC 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:11-Isa1:13\">ISA 1:11–1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:23\">EZK 18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:11\">EZK 33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:7\">HAG 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:13-Mal2:14\">MAL 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:8\">ROM 8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:10\">GAL 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:4\">1TH 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></p>\n<h2>Sacrifices and duties please God when carried out with the right attitude</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:18\">EXO 29:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:18\">PHP 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:25\">EXO 29:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:41\">EXO 29:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:9\">LEV 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev3:5\">LEV 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:3\">NUM 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:2\">NUM 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:10\">EZR 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:16\">HEB 13:16</a></p>\n<h2>Results of pleasing God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:23\">PSA 37:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:9\">1KI 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:26\">JOB 33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:7\">PRO 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:26\">ECC 7:26</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of actions that please God</h2>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:8\">PRO 15:8</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Doing God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:6\">EPH 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:17\">1JN 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those concerned to pleased God by their actions</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:19\">NEH 5:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:11\">EXO 32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:31\">NEH 13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:17\">PSA 90:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:34\">PSA 104:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:17\">DAN 9:17</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people who pleased God</h2>\n<h3>The example of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:29\">JHN 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:19\">COL 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:8\">GEN 6:8</a> <em>Noah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:12-Exod33:13\">EXO 33:12–33:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:17\">EXO 33:17</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:23\">DEU 33:23</a> <em>Naphtali</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:26\">1SA 2:26</a> <em>Samuel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:10\">1KI 3:10</a> <em>Solomon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:30\">LUK 1:30</a> <em>Mary</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:5\">HEB 11:5</a> <em>Enoch</em></p>",
